data.description: Investor's dream beautiful Pool home in the best area of central florida  close to everything avoid traffic, live minutes away  from everything   the house  features 4 bedrooms 2.5bathrooms high ceiling living room dining room  laundry room 2 car garage and a private and beautiful pool with conservation area in the back the ac unit is 11 months old   new plumbing pipes in the whole house   the inside of the house is freshly painted. this property can be use as a your primary home or can be use as a vacation home air bnb to make huge profits this is the best place for rental properties in the us   only few minutes from   Walt Disney World plus  many shopping centers  including easy access to freeways and highways      Tenats in place with 1 year least renting at $2650 a month would like to stay another year this house is already generating income owner will net about 2000 a month after taxes and insurance   this property is  Free of HOA  this property is very easy to mantain
